{"tid":2182294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小粉紅助攻】撐港人擁完整公民權 英議員寓所狂收香港寄出恐嚇信","createTime":"2020-08-31T08:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T14:18:22.000Z","uid":54373,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3db9c04118e4d1962574195944178a03734be19e","tid":2182294,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200831/EDLASLTYXFF27HA2HEJFN46VJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200831%2FEDLASLTYXFF27HA2HEJFN46VJU%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0yZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=45239587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200831%2FEDLASLTYXFF27HA2HEJFN46VJU%2F&h=aa175d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200831/EDLASLTYXFF27HA2HEJFN46VJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cUM9ztbSnZJd7X6yr7S2mswoxXg=/720x400/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRI4QVYAZRA6LFTGXCOP4NWZ7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcUM9ztbSnZJd7X6yr7S2mswoxXg%3D%2F720x400%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRI4QVYAZRA6LFTGXCOP4NWZ7Y.jpg&h=88d3d1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國下議院外交事務委員會主席董勤達（Tom Tugendhat）周日在Twitter表示，他的寓所持續收到由香港寄出的信件，雖然信件內容看似溫和，但他認為有恐嚇意味。<br />\n<br />\n董勤達上載一封信件到Twitter，指他持續收到由香港寄出的信件，雖然信件內容看似溫和，但認為是向他表達出「我知道你住在哪裏」的意思，又指中國駐英大使劉曉明的訊息十分明顯。他在帖文強調，「恐嚇民選政客是一種干擾，它必須停止」。<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席、民間組織Hong Kong Watch主席羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）回應董勤達說，他也在2018年2019年期間，收到超過20封類似信件，甚至連自己母親也收到，「很遺憾見到你現在也收到」。<br />\n董勤達一直密切關注香港事務，例如過去曾呼籲英國政府進一步讓香港民眾擁有完整的英國公民權，6月又與加拿大、澳洲及新西蘭四國的國會外交事務委員會主席，聯署去信聯合國秘書長古特雷斯（Antonio Guterres），要求派特使前往香港跟進法治與人權受破壞的問題。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter／《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"fd07de91a56a90415e8f8c47cc9bfdddb02c2bae","tid":2182294,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:19:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c08d139c69b3e11ad4c372a0c3bd11e5bd33ca43","tid":2182294,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decfa5d1039458262dc7a40c1cee1d85dbae40c6","tid":2182294,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"真係嚇鬼"},{"pid":"69e0106d207b62a83ea3d891bcbf2fedf2ee2feb","tid":2182294,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596a576e6b56663d5e5ceaf4da93b9983168f93a","tid":2182294,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6933451e710a70cd9a67a0a29cf3fb790433f7f","tid":2182294,"uid":176313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"所以話一定要將支共冚黨鏟先得"},{"pid":"4ff972b326f7cea62ee515ec04817c36baa7cd91","tid":2182294,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"到底移民關呢班支那豬咩事"},{"pid":"9d8ffcb038c3abb7ff88ad397d47ad5009e2c178","tid":2182294,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"香港寄出？<br />\n關喺香港嘅小粉紅咩事<br />\n英國嗰啲就話驚香港人嚟爭食啫<br />\n香港嗰班支那